title: The Venture Bros S03E12 Bonus Scene AS Rip - Fixed
description:
Created by chrismith85 Okay, this is a (hopefully) fixed version of the extra scene from Venture Brothers episode 312 as shown on the Adult Swim web site. The original apparently had problems with some players/codecs, so I re-encoded it using a different program. 

There are two files in this torrent. The .mpg file is fairly large (though smaller than the first one I uploaded), but should work on most players. I tested it with Media Player Classic and VLC. The .flv file is the original file downloaded
